title: I Cannot Open Some Pictures or Videos, Why?
answer:
The phone does not support the picture or video formats.  

     1、The pictures or videos are damaged.  

     2、The pictures or videos are copyright-protected.  

     3、The phone's random-access memory (RAM) is insufficient. Close some running  

third-party applications.  

     4、 An unknown error occurred in Camera or the phone's OS. This is a rare case. Restart the  

phone and try again.
